develop.commit_message:
zsh: Allow to use external script. (#453)

This patch adds support for external scripts for zsh:
Example:

complete_func() {
    echo "complete func called" > done.txt
}

eval "$(register-python-argcomplete -e complete_func arc_test)"

Fixes #452
Add support for Python 3.12 and drop EOL 3.6 and 3.7 (#449)
